<div class="spacer"></div>

<p>As color forecasts and palette predictions abound, the New Year is already supplying us with a bounty of creativity. While inspiration may be lacking after the hectic holidays, there is an abundance of peppy, pretty, and passive color to rejuvenate the spirit. From Pantone, the color authority, to two of the leading paint suppliers, here we examine their selections for 2017's color of the year. Each quite different and unique unto themselves, there is a vast variety of color available to pique interest in what the new year has to offer. </p>
<div class="spacer"></div>
			
<p>Journey with us as we review what some of the biggest names in color have predicted for 2017. </p>
<div class="spacer"></div>

