<p>For 2017 Benjamin Moore has named 'Shadow' as their color of the year. Allusive and enigmatic, here is a shade that plays with the balance of dark and light. As a master of ambiance, 'Shadow' ebbs and flows through all spaces. From rich amethyst fading into lilac grey then lustrous coal, 'Shadow' is full of mystery and emotional connections. An extraordinary color, we will have to see if 'Shadow' sets the mood for the upcoming year. </p>
