<p>'Poised Taupe' is Sherwin William's 2017 color of the year. Balancing between warm and cool, this shade is a timeless neutral, remaining modern and honest in any design. As the color and design industries evolve, so too does color. However, 'Poised Taupe' is a classic that beautifully expresses a weathered sophistication. Part earthen brown, part conservative grey, 'Poised Taupe' offers a vintage vibe, a ready-to-be-lived-in attitude, and creates a complex yet cozy sanctuary. Will 2017 embrace this affection? </p>
